      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, gnomes? i'm just trying to deal with zoning laws and setbacks here. anyway, regarding those encroachments, if the city finds something is technically encroaching but it doesn't cause an actual safety hazard, how do they usually handle it? is there a process for getting a variance or an easement agreement to keep the structure in place?",
